OL,3,C'Two-tier justice': Why are the
OL,4,Cgovernment and the Sentencing Council
OL,5,Cclashing?
OL,7,FThe government and the independent
OL,8,Fbody in charge of sentencing are
OL,9,Flocked in a row over new guidelines
OL,10,Fthat say characteristics like
OL,11,Fethnicity and gender should be
OL,12,Fconsidered ahead of sentencing.
OL,14,FAfter they were set out last month,
OL,15,Fthe new principles immediately sparked
OL,16,Faccusations of "two-tier justice".
OL,18,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,19,Fresponded by saying the guidance
OL,20,Fshould be reversed.
