OL,3,C'Two-tier justice': Why are the
OL,4,Cgovernment and the Sentencing Council
OL,5,Cclashing?
OL,7,FShabana Mahmood met with Chairman of
OL,8,Fthe Sentencing Council, Lord Justice
OL,9,FWilliam Davis, and set out in a letter
OL,10,Fthat the government policy opposes
OL,11,F"differential treatment" based on race
OL,12,For ethnicity in the courts.
OL,14,FBut in correspondence published on
OL,15,FFriday, Lord Justice Davis said the
OL,16,Fguideline does not need changing.
