OL,4,Cgovernment and the Sentencing Council
OL,5,Cclashing?
OL,7,FThe Sentencing Council guidelines also
OL,8,Fsaid pre-sentence reports should be
OL,9,Fconsidered for pregnant women and
OL,10,Fmothers of children under one-year-old.
OL,12,FAccording to the latest official data,
OL,13,Fthere were 215 pregnant women in
OL,14,FEnglish prisons between April 2023 and
OL,15,FMarch 2024, and 53 children were born
OL,16,Fto mothers in custody in the same
OL,17,Fperiod.
