OL,3,C'Two-tier justice': Why are the
OL,4,Cgovernment and the Sentencing Council
OL,5,Cclashing?
OL,7,FShabana Mahmood insisted: "There will
OL,8,Fnever be a two-tier sentencing
OL,9,Fapproach under my watch."
OL,11,FShe asked the council to remove all
OL,12,Fthe groups of people listed under the
OL,13,Fpre-sentence report guidelines and to
OL,14,Fuse a wider clause instead.
OL,16,FReacting to the Sentencing Council's
OL,17,Fresponse on Friday, she said: "I am
OL,18,Fextremely disappointed by the
OL,19,Fcouncil's response. All options are on
OL,20,Fthe table and I will legislate if
OL,21,Fnecessary."
