OL,7,F"I have been clear in my view that
OL,8,Fthese guidelines represent
OL,9,Fdifferential treatment, under which
OL,10,Fsomeone's outcomes may be influenced
OL,11,Fby their race, culture or religion.
OL,13,F"This is unacceptable, and I formally
OL,14,Fset out my objections to this in a
OL,15,Fletter to the Sentencing Council last
OL,16,Fweek.
OL,18,FAfter the guidance was first
OL,19,Fpublished, the justice secretary also
OL,20,Fannounced she was reviewing the
