OL,7,FShadow Justice Secretary Robert
OL,8,FJenrick was the first to publicly
OL,9,Fcriticise the guidance, warning that
OL,10,Fwithout government action "we will
OL,11,Fhave two-tier justice under Two-Tier
OL,12,FKeir".
OL,14,FJenrick accused Mahmood of not taking
OL,15,Fenough action to override the council,
OL,16,Fsaying her "promise to legislate down
OL,17,Fthe line is too little too late".
OL,19,F"From Tuesday she will preside over a
OL,20,Fsentencing system she conceded is two-
OL,21,Ftier," he wrote in a post on X.
